<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1260] Bytes utility class changes: remove usage of ByteBuffer and provide additional ByteBuffer primitives</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1260</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Remove all references to ByteBuffer from Bytes utility class.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add putShort, putInt, putLong methods to replicate ByteBuffer functionality.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12416703">HBASE-1260</key>
            <summary>Bytes utility class changes: remove usage of ByteBuffer and provide additional ByteBuffer primitives</summary>
